message.body: Hope you can make it for drawing tonight. Sorry I missed your stew! Hope to see you soon regardless.
I hope to make it but am unsure whether I will be able to or not.
Cool. If you do come feel free to invite Hunter. I didn't have his contact. There will be boxed wine and popcorn.
I'll tell him if I see him though
I don't think I'm going to make it tonight. Let me know if you have another drawing club meeting. I hope you have fun tonight and I hope to see you soon.
Cool thanks for letting me know
Thanks for inviting me! Next time I won't be so busy I hope
Of course. And hopefully next time I'll get the invite out sooner. Later!
